@startuml
!include ../../styles/plantuml-theme.puml

left to right direction
title FIG-11-03. Online Store Kubernetes Deployment View

skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #333333
  BackgroundColor #F7F9FB
}
skinparam component {
  BorderColor #333333
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
}

cloud "Internet" as Internet

node "Kubernetes Cluster\n<<cluster>>" as Cluster {
  rectangle "Namespace: online-store-prod\n<<Namespace>>" as Namespace {
    rectangle "GatewayClass\n<<Gateway API>>" as GatewayClass
    rectangle "Store Gateway\n<<Gateway>>" as Gateway
    rectangle "Store HTTPRoute\n<<HTTPRoute>>" as HttpRoute

    rectangle "Web Service\n<<Service>>" as WebService
    rectangle "API Service\n<<Service>>" as ApiService

    rectangle "Web Deployment\n<<Deployment>>" as WebDeployment
    rectangle "Web ReplicaSet\n<<ReplicaSet>>" as WebReplicaSet
    component "web Pods\n2 replicas\n<<Pod>>" as WebPods

    rectangle "API Deployment\n<<Deployment>>" as ApiDeployment
    rectangle "API ReplicaSet\n<<ReplicaSet>>" as ApiReplicaSet
    component "api Pods\n2 replicas\n<<Pod>>" as ApiPods

    rectangle "Worker Deployment\n<<Deployment>>" as WorkerDeployment
    rectangle "Worker ReplicaSet\n<<ReplicaSet>>" as WorkerReplicaSet
    component "worker Pods\n2 replicas\n<<Pod>>" as WorkerPods
  }
}

database "Managed Order\nDatabase\noutside cluster" as OrderDatabase
cloud "Payment Provider\nSystem" as PaymentProvider
cloud "Delivery Partner\nSystem" as DeliveryPartner

Internet --> Gateway : HTTPS
GatewayClass --> Gateway : defines controller class
Gateway --> HttpRoute : accepts route
HttpRoute --> WebService : route web traffic
HttpRoute --> ApiService : route API traffic
WebDeployment --> WebReplicaSet : manages rollout
WebReplicaSet --> WebPods : maintains replicas
ApiDeployment --> ApiReplicaSet : manages rollout
ApiReplicaSet --> ApiPods : maintains replicas
WorkerDeployment --> WorkerReplicaSet : manages rollout
WorkerReplicaSet --> WorkerPods : maintains replicas
WebService --> WebPods : selects Pods
ApiService --> ApiPods : selects Pods
ApiPods --> OrderDatabase : read/write orders
ApiPods --> PaymentProvider : authorise payment
WorkerPods --> DeliveryPartner : fulfilment requests

legend bottom
Gateway API routes external HTTPS traffic through Gateway and HTTPRoute.
Deployment manages ReplicaSets; ReplicaSets maintain Pod replicas.
Service exposes stable access to selected Pods.
The managed database and provider systems are outside the cluster.
Physical node scheduling is outside this teaching view.
StatefulSet is not shown; use it when a workload needs stable identity or persistent state behaviour.
endlegend
@enduml
